title: Ready, Fire, Aim
itunes:title: Ready, Fire, Aim
description:
Episode 192 - The concept of ready, fire, aim is to start before you are ready. Because if you wait for the perfect time, you will wait forever. Lots of people say they are "planners" and that is why it is hard for them to start, when in reality it is their fear of failure. Don't hide your fear of failure by saying you are "planner"
